Spherical to cartesian multipole transformation

09 December, 2021

This example illustrates the conversion from spherical to cartesian multipoles for the collective T-matrix of a cluster, following Mun et al.(Describing Meta-Atoms Using the Exact Higher-Order Polarizability Tensors, ACS Photonics 2020, 7, 11531162).

Last run: 09 December, 2021
